00:41:19.310 --> 00:41:20.310
Ce?

466
00:41:22.646 --> 00:41:23.646
aai voi arata.

467
00:41:25.316 --> 00:41:27.193
Cred ca...

468
00:41:31.071 --> 00:41:32.406
Aici...

